Council Meetings

Regular meetings of the Council shall be held on the first and third Tuesday evenings of each calendar month at 7:00 P.M. Any regular meeting falling upon a legal holiday shall be held on the next following secular day at the same hour and place. All meetings of the Council shall be held in the City Hall, including special and adjourned meetings.

Agendas & Minutes

2023 Committees Named by the Mayor- Updated 1-16-24

Elected Officials

Each of the City's three Aldermanic Districts is represented by two Alderpersons, one elected in even-numbered years and one elected in odd-numbered years for 2-year terms.

Mayor Mike McDermott 2024-2026
